    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mazzle Christmas is a straightforward yet surprisingly challenging celebration of the simple beauty of mazes and jigsaw puzzles in a Christmas style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you need to skillfully move the puzzle pieces, find their corresponding places, and seamlessly connect the colorful parts of the maze to complete it. Afterward, guide a small ball through the maze, collecting gifts to unlock the portal to the next level, typically located at the opposite end of the maze. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the mouse to move puzzle pieces and the keyboard (WASD or arrow keys) to navigate through the different mazes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Mazzle Christmas: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 50 levels <br>• 5 kinds of labyrinths <br>• Colorful Christmas art <br>• Simple controls <br>• Christmas music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328870/extras/9867da7089ae42063684d1c214d257df.poster.avif?t=1745433604\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328870/extras/9867da7089ae42063684d1c214d257df.webm?t=1745433604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
